{
  "stem": "25178.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But then [LAUGHS] the story of my life again, my uncle-- I was making 25 guilders a week.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, my uncle said that I should pay him 20 guilders a week for room and board.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he insisted that I should buy, every Friday, flowers for my aunt because she loved flowers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And for the rest of the money, I could buy cigarettes and buy clothing. 25 guilders was not-- or five guilders pocket money, after you had to buy flowers.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Flowers were about a guilder.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So that I had no money to buy clothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My brother got fed up living with my uncle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He had a girlfriend in Brussels.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So in December of 1949 my brother decided he was going back to Belgium.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So here again, [PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] I was alone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My uncle [PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] was a strange man in the fact that my aunt complained constantly about how he was behaving when he was taking measurements of the women's coats, things like that, plus the money problems that I had.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On top of that they had hired a maid, beautiful young girl, my age.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I fell in love with her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my uncle didn't want me to date her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he never told me why.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I did it anyhow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We went in secret.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all this combination of the money, and the fights that he had with his wife, and the fact that I had to pay him so much, and I had no money of myself, and the fact that I was loving this girl and he didn't want me to.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I was-- I had to talk to somebody about it, and the only one was my brother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So one night they went to a movie.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
